{"name":"Savage Endings","permission":{"default":0,"rZlOjAFighhoFzVn":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":3},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged Spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"Each nearby creature that’s staggered (yes, including allies, even those who are dying)"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":"Each target takes 5d6 + Charisma damage [[5d6+@cha.dmg]]"},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"5d8 damage.  [[5d8+@cha.dmg]]"},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"7d10 damage.  [[7d10+@cha.dmg]]"},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"10d10 damage.   [[10d10+@cha.dmg]]"},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>The spell no longer targets your allies.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>The spell&rsquo;s damage dice increase by one size (for example, d10s to d12s).</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>When you drop one or more non-mook creatures to 0 hp with this spell, you can heal using a free recovery.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/ice-blue-3.jpg","_id":"ca7ERVHvRni1W37T"}
{"name":"Stench of Necromancy","permission":{"default":0,"rZlOjAFighhoFzVn":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You gain a random spell from the necromancer class. Whenever you take a full heal-up, randomly choose a necromancer spell of the highest level you can cast. For the rest of the day, you know this necromancer spell and can cast it according to its normal usage pattern—at-will, once per battle, recharge, or daily—when that option comes up during your chaos mage spellcasting sequence.</p>\n<p>If the necromancer spell refers to Intelligence, you can replace that ability score with references to Charisma.</p>"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"talent"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"daily"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"free"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":""},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>One battle per day, you can gain the Cackling Soliloquist talent from the necromancer class.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>While you have an <em>earth</em> or <em>metal </em>warp effect active, when an enemy in the battle drops to 0 hp, you gain temporary hit points equal to your Charisma modifier (double your Charisma modifier at 5th level;triple it at 8th level).</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>If you don’t like the first random necromancer spell you select for the day, you can determine another random necromancer spell. You’re stuck with the second one.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/fog-sky-1.jpg","_id":"csBY1L8BoaQDfiYS"}
{"name":"War Drums","permission":{"default":0,"rZlOjAFighhoFzVn":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"at-will"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged Spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":""},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":""},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":""},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":""},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":""},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":"<p>The next natural odd attack roll you or one of your allies makes this battle that hits an enemy deals 13 extra damage.</p>"},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":"23 extra damage."},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"33 extra damage."},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"53 extra damage."},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"83 extra damage."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>Add your Charisma modifier to the extra damage (double your Charisma modifier at 5th level; triple it at 8th level).</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>When you cast this spell, each nearby enemy that&rsquo;s staggered also takes 2d6 thunder damage (4d6 thunder damage at 8th level).</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>When this spell&rsquo;s effect deals the extra damage, you can roll a hard save (16+). If you succeed, the <em>war drums</em> keep beating and the effect extends to the next natural odd hit this battle! (And so on if you keep succeeding.)</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/spells/enchant-jade-3.jpg","_id":"d3AvAjCz5W8JCt7n"}
{"_id":"eHZlsbanhq3ffe7W","name":"Tortured Scream","permission":{"default":0,"rZlOjAFighhoFzVn":3},"type":"power","data":{"name":{"type":"String","label":"Name"},"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description"},"powerSource":{"type":"String","label":"Power Source","value":"class"},"powerType":{"type":"String","label":"Power Type","value":"spell"},"powerUsage":{"type":"String","label":"Power Usage","value":"at-will"},"powerLevel":{"type":"Number","label":"Level","value":1},"actionType":{"type":"String","label":"Action","value":"standard"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"Ranged Spell"},"trigger":{"type":"String","label":"Trigger","value":""},"target":{"type":"String","label":"Target","value":"One nearby enemy"},"always":{"type":"String","label":"Always","value":""},"attack":{"type":"String","label":"Attack","value":"Charisma + Level vs. MD  [[1d20+@cha.mod+@lvl+@ed]]"},"hit":{"type":"String","label":"Hit","value":"3d6 + Charisma psychic damage. [[3d6+@cha.dmg]]"},"hitEven":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Even Hit","value":""},"hitOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Natural Odd Hit","value":""},"crit":{"type":"String","label":"Crit","value":""},"miss":{"type":"String","label":"Miss","value":"Damage equal to your level. [[@lvl]]"},"missEven":{"type":"String","label":"Even Miss","value":""},"missOdd":{"type":"String","label":"Odd Miss","value":""},"cost":{"type":"String","label":"Cost","value":""},"castBroadEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Broad Effect","value":""},"castPower":{"type":"String","label":"Cast for Power","value":""},"sustainedEffect":{"type":"String","label":"Opening and Sustained Effect","value":""},"finalVerse":{"type":"String","label":"Final Verse","value":""},"special":{"type":"String","label":"Special","value":"<p>When you cast the spell, you or a willing nearby ally of your choice loses 1d6 hit points [[1d6]].</p>"},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":"6d6 damage [[6d6+@cha.dmg]] and you or ally loses 2d6 hit points.  [[2d6]]"},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"6d10 damage, [[6d10+@cha.dmg]] and you or ally loses 4d6 hit points. [[4d6]]"},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"10d10 damage [[10d10+@cha.dmg]] and you or ally loses 6d6 hit points.   [[6d6]]"},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"2d8 x 10 damage  [[2d8*10+@cha.dmg]] and you or ally loses 8d6 hit points.  [[8d6]]"},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":"<p>The spell now deals half damage on a miss.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":"<p>You or an ally now lose one less die of hit points (for example, 3d6 instead of 4d6).</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":"<p>The first time each battle you miss with this spell, if the escalation die is 3+, you can reroll the attack by having you or your ally lose the same amount of hit points again.</p>"},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":true}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/emerald_06.jpg"}
